data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN @ 2.75% for qualified VA buyers through US Home. Impressive 4 BR, 3 Bath, 3 car garage home with pride of ownership throughout. Large Master Suite with tray ceiling on the main level. Master Bath with walk-in shower and beautifully etched shower window, along with a Large walk-in closet. This home has plenty of closet space for storage.The Gourmet kitchen has impressive marble countertops, ceramic backsplash, and plenty of cabinets for that home chef. Ceramic Plank tile floors in the main living areas and LVP on the main floor bedrooms.Upstairs has a bedroom w/walk in closet, a full bath with heated floors, and a backlit mirror, tub, and separate shower to enjoy a spa experience. Separate sitting area w/potential for a 5th bedroom. Generac Guardian 22 KW whole house generator. Relax on your covered rear porch while viewing Peach, Pear, and Apple trees with Blueberries right in your own fenced-in backyard. Additional storage is available in the garage.Trane HVAC with air scrubber (Environmental Conditioning System.) Keep your lawn looking top notch with the inground sprinkler system.Wine Cooler and Deep freezer .... DO NOT CONVEY
